    shortDescription: 'Premium research-grade peptides for metabolic and obesity research.',
    longDescription: 'Explore our collection of weight loss research peptides including GLP-1 receptor agonists, NNMT inhibitors, and lipolytic compounds. All products are HPLC-verified with ≥99% purity.',
