    searchVolume: '2400',
    shortDescription: 'GHRH analogues and secretagogues for growth hormone research.',
    longDescription: 'Our growth hormone peptide collection includes GHRH analogues, ghrelin mimetics, and secretagogues for advanced endocrine and longevity research applications.',
