    primaryKeyword: 'buy bacteriostatic water uk',
    searchVolume: '5400',
    shortDescription: 'Essential supplies for peptide research and reconstitution.',
    longDescription: 'Complete your peptide research setup with our range of laboratory supplies. From USP-grade bacteriostatic water to reconstitution accessories, all products meet pharmaceutical standards.',
